I"F<h4 id="dpi-and-ppi">DPI and PPI</h4>
<ol>
  <li>PPI describes the resolution in pixels of a digital image.</li>
  <li>DPI describes the the amount of ink dots on a printed image.</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="package">Package</h4>

<h5 id="1-graphicx-package">1. graphicx package</h5>
<p>graphicx package takes care of the numbering and positioning of the image within the document.</p>
<ol>
  <li>\linewidth: the picture will be scaled to fit the width of the document, as a result, smaller
pictures are upscaled and larger pictures dowscaled respectively..</li>
  <li>
    <p>the location in the document</p>
    <ul>
      <li>h(here): same location</li>
      <li>t(top): top of page</li>
      <li>b(bottom): bottom of page</li>
      <li>p(page): on an extra page</li>
      <li>!(override): will force the specified location</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

